obbies and interests?\",\"description\":\"Please describe your hobbies and interests in detail\",\"guide\":\"Take your time to think about activities that bring you joy and relaxation\",\"lesson\":\"Understanding hobbies helps us understand personal interests and lifestyle choices\",\"questionImage\":\"/uploads/hobbies-illustration.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"rating\",\"name\":\"question_6\",\"title\":\"How would you rate your overall satisfaction?\",\"description\":\"How would you rate your overall satisfaction with our service?\",\"isRequired\":true,\"guide\":\"Consider all aspects of your experience when rating\",\"lesson\":\"Customer satisfaction is crucial for improving our services\"}],\"title\":\"Page 3\"},{\"name\":\"page_4\",\"elements\":[{\"type\":\"checkbox\",\"name\":\"question_7\",\"visibleIf\":\"if Q6 >= 4 then show Q7\",\"title\":\"Which social media platforms do you use?\",\"description\":\"Which social media platforms do you use regularly? (Select all that apply)\",\"guide\":\"Select all platforms you use at least once a week\",\"lesson\":\"Social media usage patterns help us understand communication preferences\",\"questionImage\":\"/uploads/social-media-icons.png\",\"choices\":[{\"value\":\"choice_1\",\"text\":\"Facebook\",\"score\":1},{\"value\":\"choice_2\",\"text\":\"Instagram\",\"score\":2},{\"value\":\"choice_3\",\"text\":\"Twitter\",\"score\":3},{\"value\":\"choice_4\",\"text\":\"LinkedIn\",\"score\":4},{\"value\":\"choice_5\",\"text\":\"TikTok\",\"score\":5},{\"value\":\"choice_6\",\"text\":\"YouTube\",\"score\":6},{\"value\":\"choice_7\",\"text\":\"None of the above\"}]},{\"type\":\"boolean\",\"name\":\"question_8\",\"visibleIf\":\"if Q6 >= 3 then show Q8\",\"title\":\"Would you recommend our service?\",\"description\":\"Would you recommend our service to others?\",\"isRequired\":true,\"guide\":\"Consider your overall experience when answering this question\",\"lesson\":\"Word-of-mouth recommendations are valuable for our growth\"}],\"title\":\"Pag